          APPEND |<b>Phone Nr:</b> { <lfs_a>-tlf }|       TO ls_queue-mail_body.
          APPEND |<b>Mail:</b> { <lfs_a>-zz_elg_email } | TO ls_queue-mail_body.
          APPEND '' TO ls_queue-mail_body.
          APPEND '' TO ls_queue-mail_body.
*---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
        ELSE.
*------------------------Process for Missing Info:--------------------------------------------*
          DATA(lv_missing_fields) = me->tb_check_voyado_missing( iv_guid  = CONV #( <lfs_a>-zzbpref )
                                                                iv_store  = <lfs_a>-butikk ).
          IF lv_missing_fields = 'API_ERROR'.
